{
  "texts": [
    "We observed that the reference affinity is related to the metal ion in the system, Zn(ii), and not to PG6.",
    "The structure was consequently excluded.",
    "As depicted in Fig. 2, the most common adjustment was the removal of hydrogen atoms from the initial PDBbind geometry.",
    "This amounts to almost 75% of the modifications.",
    "It has been pointed out that libraries such as PDBbind possess biased datasets in terms of binding configurations 31."
  ]
}